---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy | GST HSN Lookup';
const description = 'Privacy Policy for GST HSN Lookup — how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our free GST tools.';
const lastUpdated = '18 June 2025';
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-base mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to <strong>GST HSN Lookup</strong> ("we", "our", or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you visit our website and use our free GST tools (GST Calculator, HSN Code Lookup, GSTIN Validator).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-base mb-2">2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>
          Our tools (GST Calculator, HSN Lookup, GSTIN Validator) operate entirely in your browser. <strong>No data you enter into these tools is transmitted to our servers.</strong> All calculations and lookups happen locally on your device.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-base mb-2 mt-4">2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p>
          When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information through third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Google Analytics 4:</strong> We use GA4 to understand how visitors use our site. GA4 collects anonymised data such as pages visited, time on site, device type, and approximate geographic location (country/city level). This data is processed by Google in accordance with their Privacy Policy. You can opt out using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Our website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect access logs and security-related data as part of their infrastructure services.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use a single cookie (<code>theme</code>) stored in your browser's <code>localStorage</code> to remember your dark/light mode preference. This is a functional cookie and does not track you across websites. Google Analytics may set its own cookies (<code>_ga</code>, <code>_gid</code>) for analytics purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">4. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information collected to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Understand how our tools are used and improve them</li>
          <li>Monitor website performance and security</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">5. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., gst.gov.in, cbic.gov.in). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those websites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          Since our tools process all data locally in your browser, your financial and tax data never leaves your device. We implement reasonable technical measures to protect our website infrastructure.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our website is not directed at children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-base mb-3">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contact" class="text-accent hover:underline">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
